tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE high_risk_patients (
  patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_name VARCHAR(255),
  age INT,
  risk_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE outreach_programs (
    program_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    program_name VARCHAR(50),
    program_description TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE patient_history (
    record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    diagnosis VARCHAR(100),
    treatment_plan TEXT,
    diagnosis_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE HighRiskPatients (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    condition VARCHAR(50),
    risk_score INT
);

CREATE TABLE OutreachPrograms (
    program_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    program_name VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE PatientHistory (
    history_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    diagnosis VARCHAR(100),
    treatment TEXT,
    outcome VARCHAR(50)
);
